          <row>
            <entry><guimenuitem>Display Modification</guimenuitem></entry>

            <entry>Setting the Display Modification option to
            <emphasis>Selected</emphasis> will display the time and the author
            of the last change for the current segment. Setting it
            to<emphasis> All </emphasis>shows this information for all
            segments and <emphasis>None</emphasis> turns this option
            off.</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </table>
  </section>

